data.title: Clark Gable residence, Beverly Hills
data.meta_description: Title supplied by cataloger.A set of steps that lead up to Clark Gable's residence, located at 1115 San Ysidro Drive in Beverly Hills. A happy dog is seen on the landing. Photograph dated August 9, 1932.
